OOC: Here goes my intro post...

BIC:

  The Predacons had finnally arrived, they knew not the exact location in 
time, but they had escaped into the past.  But thier journey had not been 
uneventful, due to an unplanned fight on board with the former crew, the 
ship was noe plummeting towards the earth.

  Upon re-entry the air around the ship's hull burst into flames, giving the 
ship an image of a giant fireball heading towards the ground. Screaming over 
the souther sky, Razorclaw was at least able to adjust course to land them 
in the water.   The co-ordinates showed that they would be landing close to 
what would be called the Azores Islands.
